title: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3 is the Best Marvel Movie in Years
description:
This video is sponsored by Nebula. Get a GREAT deal on Nebula now: https://go.nebula.tv/captainmidnight
James Gunn's Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3 stands out in the crowd of MCU movies, but I think it's more interesting as the capper to a great trilogy. In this video I go over the "final" chapter for Rocket Raccoon, Star Lord, Drax, Groot and the rest of the crew.
